repos.name: javascript-calculator
repos.description: JavaScript Calculator is a lightweight and efficient calculator application designed to perform basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. Built using JavaScript, HTML and CSS, this calculator offers a clean and intuitive interface

repos.name: javascript-clock
repos.description: A modern, responsive digital clock built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It displays the current time and updates every second, featuring a sleek design and adaptable layout for various screen sizes.

repos.name: javascript-text-encryption
repos.description: A JavaScript library designed for secure text encryption and decryption. It provides robust algorithms and utilities to ensure sensitive data is protected during transmission and storage

repos.name: javascript-timer
repos.description: A simple, responsive countdown timer built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features pause and play functionality with an alert when time runs out.

repos.name: javascript-xo-game
repos.description: A classic Tic-Tac-Toe (XO) game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features a responsive board, interactive gameplay, win detection, and a restart option.

repos.name: php-admin-panel
repos.description: PHP Admin Panel is a web application built with PHP, offering a customizable admin dashboard. It includes features like user alerts, data tables, a dynamic menu, and a banner for enhanced usability.

repos.name: php-authentication
repos.description: The PHP Authentication System is a secure solution built with PHP and MySQL for managing user access. It supports user registration, login, and logout with a clean design and essential security measures. Perfect for web applications needing user authentication.

repos.name: php-database-manager
repos.description: The Query class is a versatile PHP tool using mysqli for database management. It handles essential CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) and includes methods for user authentication and password hashing, making database interactions and user management simple and secure.

repos.name: php-mysql-marketplace
repos.description: A robust marketplace platform using PHP and MySQL. Users can create accounts, list products, and handle transactions. Key features include user registration, product listings, search and filtering, a shopping cart, and order management. Ideal for building a complete e-commerce solution.

repos.name: php-user-admin-roles
repos.description: A comprehensive user management system developed using PHP. It provides important functions for user registration, login, role management and user blocking, serving both regular users and admins.

repos.name: template-admin-panel
repos.description: AdminLTE is a flexible and fully responsive admin dashboard template built on Bootstrap 4. It features a clean, modern design and supports various screen sizes. With components like widgets, charts, and forms, it’s ideal for creating customizable and user-friendly admin panels.

repos.name: template-html-css-form
repos.description: A stylish login form template designed with HTML, CSS. Features modern UI elements, responsive design, and smooth animations. Ideal for integrating into any web application requiring a clean and user-friendly login interface.

repos.name: template-mobile-menu
repos.description: A simple and responsive mobile menu template using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features a navigation bar that adapts to both desktop and mobile screens, with a collapsible menu button for mobile views.

repos.name: template-personal-website
repos.description: A clean and responsive personal website showcasing my work as a Full-Stack Developer. Visit Iqbolshoh.uz for more information.

repos.name: website-english-platform
repos.description: English Learning Platform 🌟 — A platform to expand vocabulary, improve sentences, and enhance reading skills. Users can add words, sentences, and texts, and test their knowledge. Materials are downloadable as PDFs. 🚀

repos.name: website-samarkand-travel
repos.description: Samarkand Travel Guide: Discover the rich history, iconic landmarks, and vibrant museums of Samarkand. This guide provides essential information for exploring this historic city, from its ancient architecture to cultural attractions and local tours.
